data.description: Immaculate 3 Bed, 2 Bath Home - Fully Furnished (includes everything in the home) and Move-In Ready! Welcome to your dream home, fully equipped and ready for you to settle right in. This 2006-built gem offers a blend of modern comfort and thoughtful features that will surely impress. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the spacious and inviting living areas; this home provides ample space for families, guests, or even a home office. The kitchen is a true highlight, featuring elegant granite counters and a suite of stainless steel appliances, including a refrigerator, washer, and dryer. The adjacent dining area is perfect for both everyday meals and entertaining. This home comes complete with many valuable extras: a convenient Ring doorbell for added security, all-new blinds for privacy and light control, and a water softener and RO system for enhanced water quality. The exterior of the property is equally impressive, with professionally landscaped front and backyards offering a tranquil retreat and fantastic curb appeal. The 2-car garage provides secure parking and additional storage space.
